This roll bundles the bbftp and bbcp file transfer programs.  To install,
execute these instructions on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a frontend),
starting in this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll data-transfer
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll data-transfer | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs environment module files
in /opt/modulefiles/applications/{bbcp,bbftp}.
